name: Donnie
description: Donnie was born into a dysfunctional family. His whole life is a robbery, and then a prison. One night Donnie was hiding from the police in a monastery. The monks invited him to stay with them, he decided that this is a great place to hide from the police. Months passed and he did not notice how he became a monk. In his heart he remained a bully, a bully who brings goodness and peace.
